{
  "text": "Students perceive explanation not just as an end-product, but as a process that requires diverse cognitive and social interactions including troubleshooting, justification, communication, trust, and so on, and a knowledge transfer process from an explainer (AI system) to an explained (student) (Miller, 2019; Srinivasan & Chander, 2021).",
